title: 120: Week 3 NFL Preview
itunes:title: 120: Week 3 NFL Preview
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks get you ready for this weekend's action by analyzing the biggest storylines from every game. The guys also debate if teams really should invest heavily in a quarterback before they pick the top week 4 college football games.
